ptex
------------------------------------------
Ptex is a texture mapping system developed by Walt Disney Animation Studios
for production-quality rendering.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.6-1
  libPtex-devel-2.5.1-1bl1
  libPtex2.5-2.5.1-1bl1
  libdeflate0-1.25-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.6-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/wdas/ptex

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/wdas/ptex/archive/refs/tags/v2.5.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ptex-2.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ptex-2.5.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ptex-2.5.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ptex-2.5.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libPtex2.5-2.5.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libPtex-devel-2.5.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ptex)
  /usr/bin/ptxinfo.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ptex.README
  /usr/share/doc/ptex/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/ptex/README.md

(libPtex2.5)
  /usr/bin/cygPtex-2.5.dll

(libPtex-devel)
  /usr/include/PtexExports.h
  /usr/include/PtexHalf.h
  /usr/include/PtexInt.h
  /usr/include/PtexPlatform.h
  /usr/include/PtexUtils.h
  /usr/include/PtexVersion.h
  /usr/include/Ptexture.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-exports-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-exports.cmake
  /usr/lib/libPtex.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ptex.pc

